                <div style="text-align:left">
                    <h3><b>Events</b></h3>
                    <p><u>Purpose: The events page allows you to create, view, and manage events</u></p>
                    <p><u>Actions: What can you do with the events page?</u></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>"Create an Event" - You can create an event by either...
                            <ol>
                                <li>Clicking a day with no events which will direct you to a form to create an event</li>
                                OR
                                <li>Clicking a day with events, and then clicking the "Add New Event" button</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>"View an Event" - You can view an event's information by...
                            <ol>
                                <li>Clicking the day the event is scheduled</li>
                                <li>Then, click the specific event you wish to view</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>"Edit an Event" - You can edit an existing event by...
                            <ol>
                                <li>Clicking the day the event is scheduled</li>
                                <li>Then, click the specific event you wish to edit</li>
                                <li>Then, click "Edit Event"</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>"Delete an Event" - You can delete an event by...
                            <ol>
                                <li>Clicking the day the event is scheduled</li>
                                <li>Then, click the specific event you wish to delete</li>
                                <li>Then, click "Delete Event"</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>"RSVP for an Event" - You can let the event planners know you will be attending an event by RSVPing. You can RSVP for an event by...
                            <ol>
                                <li>Clicking the day the event is scheduled</li>
                                <li>Then, click the specific event you wish to RSVP for</li>
                                <li>Then, click "RSVP" and pick an option</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>"Attend an Event" - You can get points for attending an event by entering the passcode for an event. You can attend an event by...
                            <ol>
                                <li>Clicking the day the event is scheduled</li>
                                <li>Then, click the specific event you wish to attend</li>
                                <li>Then, click "Attend" and submit the passcode provided for the event</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

