                        <li>"Create a Committee" - You can create a committee by clicking "Create a Committee"</li>
                        <li>"View a Committee" - You can view a committee's information by clicking "View" on the committee you wish to see. This will display 3 tables
                            <ol>
                                <li>The first table displays the total points earned by which committee events</li>
                                <li>The second table displays all the members of the current committee</li>
                                <li>The third table breaks each member's points down by which committe events they attended</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>"Edit a Committee" - You can edit an existing committee by either...
                            <ol>
                                <li>Clicking "Edit" on the committee you want to change</li>
                                OR
                                <li>Clicking "View" then "Edit" on the committee you want to change</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>"Delete an Committee" - You can delete a committee by clicking "Delete"</li>
                    </ul>

